Model fit

overfitting- good on training but bad in evaluation
or underfitting- bad on training data, could be simple

Balanced- neither under nor over

Bias & Variance

Bias- diff between predicted and actual values
if High bias, low variance- underfitting

Variance- how much performance changes if trained on diff data
to reduce, consider less features, split data multiple times
Low Bias, HIgh variance- overfitting

Balanced- low bias & low variance

